ext-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em;\">适当超计划招录。</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">三、培养年限及要求：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>1.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\">医院按照国家卫健委《住院医师规范化培训的内容与标准（试行）》和江苏省卫健委住院医师规范化培训的相关要求，制定培训计划和轮转方案，并严格按照计划对培训学员进行培训。 </span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>2.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\">住院医师规范化培训时长根据《住院医师规范化培训的内容与标准（试行）》，培训年限为三年，学员完成培训并通过各项考核者，颁发国家级《住院医师规范化培训合格证书》。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>3.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\">住培学员在我院培训期间，须履行国家规定的住院医师规范化培训期间应尽的责任和义务，并遵守医院相关管理规定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">四、盐城市一院住培基地学员的优惠政策：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>1.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">我院于<span>2019</span>年正式挂牌南京大学医学院附属盐城第一人民医院，根据盐城市政府与南京大学合作协议，凡在我院参培的住培学员可择优参加南京大学在职研究生班，结业时通过南京大学在职研究生班各项考核合格可获得“<strong>南京大学研究生</strong>”学位证。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>2.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">我院全科专业基地为盐城市最大的全科培训基地，盐城市全科医学会主任委员、盐城市全科医学研究所均在基地，多次举办省市级学术会议、师资培训、继续教育；为进一步建设全科培训基地，提高教学水平，除增加师资培训，提升基层实践基地水平外，给以全科进一步倾斜支持，包含：提高学员补助、配置导师、专项技能培训等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>3.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">我院招收的社会化学员结业后需自行择业，根据双向选择原则，毕业时考核优秀、紧缺专业的学员同等条件下我院优先录用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>五、</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">相关规定及待遇</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（一）根据《关于贯彻落实住院医师规范化培训“<strong><strong>两个同等对待</strong></strong>”政策的通知》（国卫办科教〔</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">2021</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">〕</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">18</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">号）的要求，维护学员权益，落实“两个同等对待”政策，面向社会招收的普通高校应届毕业生培训对象培训合格当年在医疗卫生机构就业的，在招聘、派遣、落户等方面，按当年应届毕业生同等对待。对经住培合格的本科学历临床医师，在人员招聘、职称晋升、岗位聘用、薪酬待遇等方面与临床医学、中医专业学位硕士研究生同等对待。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（二）医院按照国家卫健委《住院医师规范化培训的内容与标准（</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">2022</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">年版）》和江苏省卫健委住院医师规范化培训的相关要求进行轮转培训。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（三）培训年限为三年。完成培训任务，并通过结业考核者，由省卫健委颁发全国统一制式的《住院医师规范化培训合格证书》。进入培训后，因个人原因需要协议退培的，培训时长不得少于一年。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（四）委托培训学员在培训期间原人事（劳动）、工资关系不变，委托培训学员的基本工资、基础性绩效及各种社会保险仍由原单位发放。社会化学员基本工资、绩效工资及相关保险发放标准参照我院同等条件住院医师工资水平。</span><span style=\"background: white;\">社会化学员第一年实发工资约<span>5.1</span>万，五险一金及补助、绩效另算，绩效根据是否取得执医资格和工作能力表现，每年<span>2.6</span>万<span>-4</span>万，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a name=\"_GoBack\"></a></p><p>年收入按学历、是否取得执业医师、年级分层分级逐年递增，允许同时填报两个以上志愿，服从调剂。</p><p></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"background: white;\">（五）委培学员必须为派送单位在编职工或与单位签订正式聘<span style=\"color:black\">用合同的职工，委培学员培训结束后，学员均回委托培养单位工作，我院不予留用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（六）参培学员应结业当年及之后两年未通过结业考核者，如再次申请结业考核，需重新参加住院医师规范化培训，培训相关费用由个人承担。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（七）奖励性绩效由我院依据相关管理规定发放：奖励性绩效每人每月基数<span>2222</span>元；取得执业医师资格证书后，并在我院注册，每人每月增加发放<span>1000</span>元。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">除以上待遇之外，还享受以下补充待遇：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">1</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">）免费住宿或专项住宿补贴<span>3</span></span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">00</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">元</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">/</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">月；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">2</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">）伙食补贴<span>36</span></span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">0</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">元</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">/</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">月；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">3</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">）发放国庆、医师节、春节等福利；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">4</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">）培训期间各类考核优秀者均按相应标准发放额外奖励。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px 15px 16px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（<span>5</span>）同本院职工一样享受每年一次的体检。</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><br /> </span><strong><span style=\"color: black;\">六、报名：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\">委培学员由派送单位统一报名。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\">社会化学员</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">实行现场报名，下载</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">个人简历</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">表格，见附件，填写好相关资料后提交纸质档一份和电子档一份，</span><span><a href=\"mailto:%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E6%A1%A3%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%88%B0KJK8915@126.com\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>电子档提交邮箱：</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">KJK8915@126.com</span></a></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">1.</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">报名时间：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">社会化学员：<span>2023</span>年<span>6</span>月<span>1</span>日至<span>2023</span>年<span>6</span>月<span>30</span>日</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">委培学员：<span>2023</span>年<span>6</span>月<span>1</span>日至<span>2023</span>年<span>8</span>月<span>31</span>日</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">2.</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">报名及通讯地址：盐城市第一人民医院 教育处<span>(</span>盐城市毓龙西路<span>166</span>号）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">3.</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">邮编：<span>224006</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">电话：<span>0515</span>—<span>88508935</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">联系人：刘国霞、贾婧</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">4.</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">审核：医院根据报名材料对报名人员资格进行审核，社会化学员招收结合本院培训基地招生要求发布进入考核人员名单。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">社会化学员报名现场资格审核需携带下列材料：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">①</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">简历一份。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">②</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">身份证原件及复印件一份。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">③</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">近期正面免冠二寸照片</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">张。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">④</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">毕业证书及学位证书原件及复印件一份。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">⑤</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">英语、计算机等级考试合格证书原件及复印件一份。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">⑥</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">获奖证书原件及复印件一份</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 25px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>七、</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">考试</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; background: white; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(21, 21, 21); background: white;\">考试方式分笔试、技能考核和面试，内容侧重于临床专业知识、基本技能和综合素质测试。社会化学员考试具体时间和地点另行通知，免收考试费。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 25px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>八、</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">体检及录取</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">根据考试总成绩，从高分到低分按招收人数</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">∶</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">确定体检人员，体检标准参照《国家公务员录用体检通用标准（试行）》。对体检合格录取人员，按照相关规定签订培训协议，办理有关手续。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">附件</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;\" src=\"/ueditor/dialogs<!--#p8_attach#-->/fileTypeImages/icon_xls.gif\" src=\"/ueditor/dialogs<!--#p8_attach#-->/fileTypeImages/icon_xls.gif\" /><a style=\"font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;\" href=\"<!--#p8_attach#-->/cms/item/2023_06/14_08/ac2091a8e2843f01.xls\" title=\"个人简历.xls\">个人简历.xls</a></p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom: auto;text-align:left;text-indent:32px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"></span><br /></p><p><br /></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('3119','3944','1','','<!--#p8_attach#-->/cms/item/2023_06/14_16/9cc0c2330ba251af.png.cthumb.jpg','盐城市第一人民医院创建于1948年，经过七十余年的发展，现已建设成为一所集医疗、教学、科研、康复、急救为一体的三级甲等综合性医院。医院是首批国家级“住院医师规范化培训基地”、“全科医生临床培养建设基地”，承担南通大学、徐州医学院本科与研究生教学任务，及江','10.10.10.10','10.10.10.10','1686730817','<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">盐城市第一人民医院创建于<span>1948</span>年，经过七十余年的发展，现已建设成为一所集医疗、教学、科研、康复、急救为一体的三级甲等综合性医院。医院</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">是首批国家级“住院医师规范化培训基地”、“全科医生临床培养建设基地”，承担南通大学、徐州医学院本科与研究生教学任务，及江苏医药职业学院等十余所高校实习生带教工作<span>,</span>并于</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">2019</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">年正式挂牌南京大学医学院附属盐城第一人民医院。</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">医院共设有<span>4</span>个院区：主院区、北院区、五官科院区、儿童医院。</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">医院重视学科建设，建成了一批特色鲜明的重点专科，其中呼吸内科、骨科、普外科、心内科、检验科、影像科、肿瘤科、神经内科等<span>20</span>个科室被评为江苏省临床重点专科；市级临床重点专科<span>15</span>个；市医学重点学科<span>18</span>个。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"<!--#p8_attach#-->/cms/item/2023_06/14_16/9cc0c2330ba251af.png.cthumb.jpg\" title=\"微信图片_20230614084514.png\" alt=\"微信图片_20230614084514.png\" /></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">为了更好地选拔优秀人才，培养合格临床医师，我培训基地从即日起面向社会及各单位招收<span>2023</span>年度住院医师规范化培训社会化<span>/</span>单位委培养学员，现将有关事项公告如下：</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">一、基本条件：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>1.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">坚持四项基本原则，</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">拥护党的路线、方针、政策，</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">遵纪守法，品行端正，无违法违纪行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>2.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">高等院校西医医学类相应专业，普通本科以上学历的应、往届毕业生。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>3.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">身心健康，能胜任住院医师规范化培训的临床学习和工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>4.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">外语要求：原则上具备大学英语四级及以上合格证，报考紧缺专业外语要求可适当放宽。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>5.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">计算机水平达到国家或省计算机等级考试一级。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">附加条件<span>1.</span>年龄要求：原则上本科生不超过<span>30</span>周岁，研究生不超过<span>35</span>周岁，紧缺专业年龄适当放宽。<span>2.</span>单位委培培训学员须出具在职证明及单位委培公函。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">二、招收专业：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">全科、内科、外科、外科（神经外科方向）、外科（胸心外科方向）、外科（泌尿外科方向）、外科（整形外科方向）、骨科、眼科、耳鼻喉科、妇产科、神经内科、急诊医学科、重症医学科、儿科、皮肤科、麻醉科、康复医学科、放射科、放射肿瘤科、超声医学科、检验医学科、核医学科、临床病理科，共<span>24</span>个培训专业。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">招生计划表如下：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px 15px 21px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em;\">盐城市第一人民医院招收<span>2023</span>年度住院医师规范化培训学员计划表</p><table><tbody><tr style=\";height:40px\" class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"40\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-left: 2px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em;\">序号</p></td><td width=\"185\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-image: initial; border-left: none; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin: 15px 5px 15px 8px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em;\">招生专业</p></td><td width=\"85\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-image: initial; border-left: none; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin: 15px 2px 15px 4px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em